    body
        div(data-role="page", id="landing")
            div(data-role="content")
                div
                    img(style="width: 100%; height: px", src="/img/Wobblies_Logo.png")
                    h3 Steps to being slim
                div(data-role="controlgroup", data-type="horizontal")
                    ul(data-role="listview", data-divider-theme="b", data-inset="true")
                        li(data-theme="c") Take a picture of your belly... and repeat
                        li(data-theme="c") Watch the video of your belly's progress.
                        li(data-theme="c") Get inspired and get thin!
                    p You can use wobblies privately for a period, taking pictures of your belly and watching them play back as a (rather primitive - for now) video.<br /><br />
                div(data-role="collapsible", data-collapsed="false")
                    h2 Thought for the Day
                    p
                        #{thought_for_the_day}
                div(data-role="collapsible", data-collapsed="true")
                    h2 What is Wobblies?
                    p
                        |wobblies is a mobile app that was developed in two days at the&nbsp;
                        a(href="http://nhshackday.com/")
                            |NHS Hackday
                        |. It is deliberately "in your face"
                        |app, pulling no punches about trying to draw people's attention to - and then combat - obesity, which costs the NHS Â£2
                        |billion/year (more than the Dilnot <img src="img/FatMan.png" style="width:40%; float:right;"></img>report says it would cost to properly fund social care).<br /><br />
                        |You can use it privately for a period, taking pictures of your belly and watching them play back as a (rather primitive - for now) video.<br /><br />
                        |After the introductory period you will be forced to <em>pledge</em> - promise to show someone (who will normally be making the same promise to you)
                        |three months worth of belly videos.  And just in case that doesn't focus the mind, if you fail to keep coming back and
                        |take the photos, you will be have to make a contribution to a good cause of your choice.
                div(data-role="controlgroup")
                    a(href="#", data-role="button") Upload a Private Photo
                    a(href='#video', data-role="button") Show my Video
                    a(href="#pledgeto", data-role="button") Be Brave and Pledge
        div(data-role="page", id="pledgeto")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Pledge to whom?
            div(data-role="content")
                h4 Good on you!
                p The first step to a better body has been taken.
                p The person to whom you make your pledge will receive an email telling them that you are determined to lose that spare tyre, and that in 3 months time they will get a video showing what a brilliant job you have done.
                p How would you like to choose the person you want to make your pledge to?
                div(data-role="controlgroup")
                    a(href="#email", data-role="button") Email
                    a(href="#comingsoon", data-role="button") Facebook
                    a(href="#comingsoon", data-role="button") Twitter
                    a(href="#match", data-role="button") Match Me!
        div(data-role="page", id="comingsoon")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 We are sorry
            div(data-role="content")
                h4 We are working our spare tyres off trying to add and improve our service.<br /><br />Sorry but the feature that you are requesting is currently not available.
                a(href="#pledgeto", data-role="button") Go Back
        div(data-role="page", id="email")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Pledge to email
            div(data-role="content")
                form(action="send.php", action="post")
                    div(data-role="fieldcontainer")
                        label(for="email") Email
                        input(type="email", id="email", name="email")
        div(data-role="page", id="video")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 My Progress
            div(data-role="content")
                <center>
                <video width="90%"controls="controls">
                <source src="http://192.168.49.149:3000/video/user" type="video/mp4" />
                </video>
                </center>
                <a href="#landing" data-role="button">Go Back</a>
        div(data-role="page", id="match")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Find a fat friend
            div(data-role="content")
                h2 How would you describe your figure?
                ul(data-role="listview", data-divider-theme="b", data-inset="true")
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other2", data-transition="slide") Plumptious
                        span(class="ui-li-count") BMI 25+
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other2", data-transition="slide") Quite Chubby
                        span(class="ui-li-count") BMI 30+
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other2", data-transition="slide") Really Porky
                        span(class="ui-li-count") BMI 35+
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other2", data-transition="slide") Fat Bastard
                        span(class="ui-li-count") BMI 40+
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other2", data-transition="slide") Jabba the Hutt
                        span(class="ui-li-count") BMI 45+
                a(href="http://www.bmi-calculator.net/", data-role="button", data-transition="slide") Calculate your BMI
        div(data-role="page", id="other2")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Find a fat friend
            div(data-role="content")
                h2 How old are you?
                ul(data-role="listview", data-divider-theme="b", data-inset="true")
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Younger than springtime
                        span(class="ui-li-count") < 20
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Spring Chicken
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 20's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") The old 30s
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 30's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Feeling the pace
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 40's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") The new 30s
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 50's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Retirement age (now)
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 60's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Retirement age (soon)
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 70's
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other3", data-transition="slide") Silver surfer
                        span(class="ui-li-count") 80's
        div(data-role="page", id="other3")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Find a fat friend
            div(data-role="content")
                h2 Are you a Man/Woman?
                ul(data-role="listview", data-divider-theme="b", data-inset="true")
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#forfeit", data-transition="slide") Man
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#other4", data-transition="slide") Woman
        div(data-role="page", id="other4")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Find a fat friend
            div(data-role="content")
                h2 Are you a mother?
                a(data-role="button", data-transition="slide", href="#forfeit") Yes
                a(data-role="button", data-transition="slide", href="#forfeit") No
        div(data-role="page", id="forfeit")
            div(data-role="header")
                h1 Take your pick
            div(data-role="content")
                h2 In the _unlikely_ event that you fail to honour your pledge you need to promise to make a payment to one of these three destinations:
                ul(data-role="listview", data-divider-theme="b", data-inset="true")
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#", data-transition="slide") NHS preventative fund
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#", data-transition="slide") A charity of your choice...
                    li(data-theme="c")
                        a(href="#", data-transition="slide") A cause you disapprove of... (many economists feel that the fear of paying for a cause you do not sympathise with is a better motivator than simply spending money)
